1
00:00:08,260 --> 00:00:11,220
♪Dark clouds shroud the long trail
where the sun descends♪

2
00:00:11,260 --> 00:00:13,980
♪Must we only meet by chance
and never again?♪

3
00:00:14,020 --> 00:00:16,900
♪To be parted forever in an instant♪

4
00:00:16,940 --> 00:00:19,660
♪Time flies never to be recalled♪

5
00:00:19,700 --> 00:00:22,700
♪When your smile is embedded
in the starry night♪

6
00:00:22,740 --> 00:00:25,740
♪We are puppets of twisted fates♪

7
00:00:25,780 --> 00:00:28,620
♪Constantly intertwining♪

8
00:00:28,660 --> 00:00:31,660
♪Dissolving in the crowd♪

9
00:00:31,700 --> 00:00:34,940
♪Perhaps out of reach and out of sight♪

10
00:00:34,940 --> 00:00:37,260
♪Constantly flashing through my dreams♪

11
00:00:37,300 --> 00:00:45,100
♪The sudden icy wind blurs my vision♪

12
00:00:46,980 --> 00:00:50,660
♪The rain drew that day to an end♪

13
00:00:50,700 --> 00:00:54,380
♪How I wish your beauty♪

14
00:00:54,380 --> 00:00:59,460
♪I want to love you,
love you, love you, love you♪

15
00:01:06,660 --> 00:01:10,820
[My Divine Emissary]

16
00:01:10,940 --> 00:01:13,820
[Episode 21]

17
00:01:14,220 --> 00:01:17,900
[Shoukang Palace]

18
00:01:30,240 --> 00:01:31,040
Yan.

19
00:01:31,400 --> 00:01:32,240
Mother.

20
00:01:32,560 --> 00:01:33,320
Yan.

21
00:01:34,080 --> 00:01:34,760
Yan.

22
00:01:34,960 --> 00:01:36,600
My little Yan fell into the water.

23
00:01:36,600 --> 00:01:37,880
- Who's going to save him?
- Mother.

24
00:01:39,440 --> 00:01:40,200
Yan.

25
00:01:40,880 --> 00:01:41,680
I'm here.

26
00:01:42,600 --> 00:01:44,520
I'm sorry. It's mother's fault.

27
00:01:45,640 --> 00:01:47,320
Brother, please don't kill Yan.

28
00:01:47,440 --> 00:01:48,440
I'm begging you.

29
00:01:48,440 --> 00:01:49,760
Please spare my Yan.

30
00:01:52,520 --> 00:01:53,440
Yan.

31
00:01:57,440 --> 00:01:58,320
Yan.

32
00:02:02,000 --> 00:02:03,040
Yan.

33
00:02:06,360 --> 00:02:07,720
Are you alright?

34
00:02:12,400 --> 00:02:13,639
I'm fine.

35
00:02:14,199 --> 00:02:15,320
That's good.

36
00:02:16,200 --> 00:02:17,360
That's good.

37
00:02:25,000 --> 00:02:26,240
Where is your uncle?

38
00:02:26,760 --> 00:02:27,560
How is he?

39
00:02:28,680 --> 00:02:30,080
Cui Anshi plotted a rebellion.

40
00:02:32,560 --> 00:02:33,680
It was an unforgivable crime.

41
00:02:35,440 --> 00:02:37,120
The palace is a dangerous place.

42
00:02:38,240 --> 00:02:41,760
I thought if everything
was going his way.

43
00:02:42,720 --> 00:02:44,160
With the power of the Cui family,

44
00:02:44,760 --> 00:02:46,080
he could protect my son.

45
00:02:46,520 --> 00:02:47,920
But I never thought

46
00:02:48,280 --> 00:02:50,440
that his heart could never be satisfied.

47
00:02:52,720 --> 00:02:53,680
Yan.

48
00:02:54,440 --> 00:02:55,360
Mother.

49
00:02:59,720 --> 00:03:01,400
Your son has grown up now.

50
00:03:07,000 --> 00:03:08,080
From now on,

51
00:03:11,840 --> 00:03:13,960
it's my turn to protect you.

52
00:03:16,280 --> 00:03:17,280
Yan.

53
00:03:18,880 --> 00:03:19,880
Yan.

54
00:03:27,080 --> 00:03:28,120
Yan.

55
00:03:32,440 --> 00:03:33,000
Wan.

56
00:03:33,240 --> 00:03:34,120
Huai'an.

57
00:03:47,760 --> 00:03:50,840
My father, is he...

58
00:03:52,640 --> 00:03:54,200
Chancellor Cui has been imprisoned
in the dungeon,

59
00:03:54,640 --> 00:03:55,840
awaiting trial by
the Three Judicial Officials.

60
00:03:57,720 --> 00:03:59,640
The rebellion is widely implicated.

61
00:04:00,080 --> 00:04:03,200
His Majesty will investigate
seriously this time.

62
00:04:04,520 --> 00:04:05,040
Wan.

63
00:04:08,440 --> 00:04:09,840
According to the law, nine generations

64
00:04:09,860 --> 00:04:11,200
should be implicated
for the crime of rebellion.

65
00:04:12,520 --> 00:04:13,960
His Majesty has already
shown great mercy.

66
00:04:15,000 --> 00:04:17,560
Those involved in the rebellion,
will be punished according to law.

67
00:04:18,720 --> 00:04:20,880
The other members of the Cui family
will be demoted to commoners,

68
00:04:22,440 --> 00:04:24,000
and will be banned from
official positions for three generations.

69
00:04:41,960 --> 00:04:43,080
I'm back.

70
00:04:47,920 --> 00:04:48,600
Em...

71
00:04:48,600 --> 00:04:49,800
Emissary?

72
00:04:51,120 --> 00:04:51,680
What?

73
00:04:51,920 --> 00:04:52,840
Can't recognize me?

74
00:04:52,960 --> 00:04:53,680
Well...

75
00:04:54,440 --> 00:04:55,280
But...

76
00:04:59,120 --> 00:04:59,880
Stop going around.

77
00:05:00,040 --> 00:05:00,960
It's making me dizzy.

78
00:05:01,600 --> 00:05:02,520
It's me.

79
00:05:02,920 --> 00:05:03,920
Emissary Xiao.

80
00:05:04,240 --> 00:05:05,520
Totally authentic.

81
00:05:05,520 --> 00:05:06,880
It's the voice of Emissary Xiao

82
00:05:07,320 --> 00:05:08,560
and his appearance as well.

83
00:05:09,120 --> 00:05:11,760
But why are you a woman?

84
00:05:13,640 --> 00:05:14,480
Well...

85
00:05:14,880 --> 00:05:16,360
I've always been a girl.

86
00:05:17,440 --> 00:05:18,200
Where's Zhou Quan?

87
00:05:19,920 --> 00:05:20,840
Zhou Quan.

88
00:05:21,640 --> 00:05:23,400
Don't you know I'm back?

89
00:05:23,400 --> 00:05:24,760
Hurry up and welcome me back!

90
00:05:28,880 --> 00:05:29,760
Where is she?

91
00:05:33,080 --> 00:05:34,040
Are you...

92
00:05:34,040 --> 00:05:35,720
not hiding a surprise for me,

93
00:05:35,720 --> 00:05:36,400
are you?

94
00:05:37,280 --> 00:05:37,760
Alright.

95
00:05:38,520 --> 00:05:39,840
But just keep it low-key, alright?

96
00:05:41,520 --> 00:05:42,280
- Zhou Quan.
- Emissary Xiao.

97
00:05:42,280 --> 00:05:42,840
Emissary Xiao.

98
00:05:42,840 --> 00:05:44,160
- Emissary Xiao.
- Zhou Quan.

99
00:05:45,120 --> 00:05:45,880
Zhou Quan.

100
00:05:45,880 --> 00:05:46,800
I'm back.

101
00:06:01,240 --> 00:06:02,640
Emissary Xiao.

102
00:06:03,000 --> 00:06:03,960
Emissary Xiao.

103
00:06:04,280 --> 00:06:05,560
Zhou Quan, she...

104
00:06:06,520 --> 00:06:08,000
She's gone.

105
00:06:10,040 --> 00:06:10,840
That day...

106
00:06:11,120 --> 00:06:13,720
Zhou Quan went to the Empress's chamber
to deliver a talisman.

107
00:06:14,120 --> 00:06:15,400
But after she left,

108
00:06:15,400 --> 00:06:16,840
she never came back.

109
00:06:18,120 --> 00:06:19,760
When we found her,

110
00:06:20,360 --> 00:06:21,960
she had already been killed

111
00:06:21,960 --> 00:06:23,280
by Cui Anyu's imperial guards.

112
00:06:23,920 --> 00:06:25,240
The high priest said,

113
00:06:25,240 --> 00:06:27,520
that you'd want
to see her one last time,

114
00:06:27,920 --> 00:06:30,160
so he placed her in this ice coffin.

115
00:06:41,560 --> 00:06:42,640
Zhou Quan.

116
00:06:44,680 --> 00:06:45,760
Zhou Quan.

117
00:06:53,520 --> 00:06:54,600
Guard Kong.

118
00:06:54,760 --> 00:06:56,960
Can you help me wake Zhou Quan up?

119
00:06:57,760 --> 00:06:58,800
It seems like everyone...

120
00:06:58,800 --> 00:06:59,760
really enjoys

121
00:06:59,760 --> 00:07:01,280
playing this kind of joke
on me recently.

122
00:07:01,600 --> 00:07:03,960
We always had so much fun together.

123
00:07:03,960 --> 00:07:05,520
This must be her way of teasing me.

124
00:07:06,240 --> 00:07:08,040
Quickly, help me tell her...

125
00:07:08,040 --> 00:07:09,720
this is not funny at all.

126
00:07:29,880 --> 00:07:30,560
Zhou Quan.

127
00:07:32,440 --> 00:07:33,040
Look.

128
00:07:35,480 --> 00:07:37,000
This is your favorite hairpin.

129
00:07:51,080 --> 00:07:52,280
You look so beautiful with it on.

130
00:07:52,280 --> 00:07:52,920
Do you know that?

131
00:07:56,400 --> 00:07:57,160
It's beautiful.

132
00:07:58,000 --> 00:07:59,320
Very beautiful.

133
00:08:05,920 --> 00:08:07,200
There's nothing in the palace...

134
00:08:07,200 --> 00:08:08,760
that I don't know about.

135
00:08:08,760 --> 00:08:10,700
[Eunuch Quarters]

136
00:08:11,520 --> 00:08:12,240
This is for you.

137
00:08:13,400 --> 00:08:14,160
What's this?

138
00:08:14,440 --> 00:08:15,920
This is the healing ointment
bestowed by His Majesty.

139
00:08:18,600 --> 00:08:19,440
My guard,

140
00:08:23,320 --> 00:08:24,000
thanks.

141
00:08:35,280 --> 00:08:37,960
I'm your lifesaver now.

142
00:08:38,760 --> 00:08:40,679
Aren't you going to offer yourself to me

143
00:08:40,679 --> 00:08:41,760
to be even? Right?

144
00:08:41,760 --> 00:08:42,440
Okay.

145
00:08:45,360 --> 00:08:46,360
I like you.

146
00:08:47,159 --> 00:08:48,679
I just want to tell you I like you.

147
00:08:49,280 --> 00:08:50,559
You don't have to rush to answer me.

148
00:08:51,520 --> 00:08:52,320
Guard Kong.

149
00:08:53,799 --> 00:08:55,360
I already have an answer

150
00:08:55,520 --> 00:08:56,760
for your question you asked me today.

151
00:08:56,920 --> 00:08:57,640
What is it?

152
00:08:59,440 --> 00:09:00,840
I'll tell you when you get back.

153
00:09:15,480 --> 00:09:16,240
Quan...

154
00:09:20,200 --> 00:09:20,880
Look.

155
00:09:24,600 --> 00:09:25,840
I remember...

156
00:09:27,280 --> 00:09:28,640
you said before...

157
00:09:29,040 --> 00:09:32,640
that you wanted to try these sneakers
when you had the chance.

158
00:09:33,680 --> 00:09:34,320
Look.

159
00:09:34,720 --> 00:09:35,400
Today,

160
00:09:37,240 --> 00:09:39,600
I help you put them on.

161
00:09:48,040 --> 00:09:49,640
Do you feel extremely cold

162
00:09:51,000 --> 00:09:52,600
when you're lying on it?

163
00:09:54,680 --> 00:09:56,080
With these shoes,

164
00:09:57,040 --> 00:10:00,320
your feet can be a little warmer.

165
00:10:02,560 --> 00:10:03,440
If...

166
00:10:04,600 --> 00:10:06,880
I had put them on you earlier,

167
00:10:08,440 --> 00:10:10,480
could you have run faster

168
00:10:12,880 --> 00:10:16,040
the day you were chased?

169
00:10:16,400 --> 00:10:17,400
Then you wouldn't have...

170
00:10:21,360 --> 00:10:23,240
It was my bad.

171
00:10:53,440 --> 00:10:54,480
The Emissary has appeared.

172
00:10:54,480 --> 00:10:55,760
Hurry up and step back!

173
00:10:56,400 --> 00:10:58,800
Forgive us, Emissary.

174
00:11:03,960 --> 00:11:06,200
Does this mean I'm disappearing?

175
00:11:10,640 --> 00:11:13,680
Although I should be grateful
for the timely rain,

176
00:11:14,400 --> 00:11:15,280
but this time,

177
00:11:15,640 --> 00:11:17,120
I'd completely disappeared.

178
00:11:18,040 --> 00:11:19,520
What does that mean?

179
00:11:20,640 --> 00:11:21,760
Can I go back?

180
00:11:22,440 --> 00:11:25,400
Or will I disappear forever?

181
00:11:26,480 --> 00:11:27,560
It's been so long.

182
00:11:27,920 --> 00:11:29,880
I should be happy to go back.

183
00:11:30,760 --> 00:11:31,840
However,

184
00:11:32,600 --> 00:11:33,320
if I really

185
00:11:33,320 --> 00:11:35,240
suddenly disappear from this world,

186
00:11:36,120 --> 00:11:37,360
what is Qi Yan going to do?

187
00:11:38,000 --> 00:11:39,360
Will he hate me?

188
00:11:42,800 --> 00:11:44,080
Greetings to Your Majesty.

189
00:11:52,000 --> 00:11:52,720
Mengmeng.

190
00:12:04,200 --> 00:12:05,920
I will definitely avenge Zhou Quan.

191
00:12:08,000 --> 00:12:09,560
I'll let her leave peacefully.

192
00:12:10,600 --> 00:12:11,560
What about Kong An?

193
00:12:12,200 --> 00:12:13,160
Is he alright?

194
00:12:15,920 --> 00:12:17,400
I've never seen him like this,

195
00:12:18,600 --> 00:12:19,800
moping around all day.

196
00:12:21,160 --> 00:12:23,320
It just shows how important
Zhou Quan was to him.

197
00:12:28,520 --> 00:12:32,400
Perhaps Zhou Quan just went on a trip

198
00:12:33,000 --> 00:12:34,280
and would be back soon.

199
00:12:35,480 --> 00:12:37,280
We will definitely see her again.

200
00:12:38,360 --> 00:12:39,000
Of course.

201
00:12:40,080 --> 00:12:41,120
We definitely will.

202
00:12:44,360 --> 00:12:47,640
Do you know how I felt the other day

203
00:12:48,240 --> 00:12:49,520
when you collapsed in my arms?

204
00:12:51,120 --> 00:12:52,040
What did you feel?

205
00:12:55,080 --> 00:12:56,880
I felt like the sky was falling,

206
00:12:57,960 --> 00:12:59,760
crushing me so hard
till I couldn't breathe.

207
00:13:00,960 --> 00:13:03,240
I couldn't even believe
that you were going to leave me.

208
00:13:04,640 --> 00:13:05,680
Later,

209
00:13:05,960 --> 00:13:07,640
Qi Su locked me in the room.

210
00:13:08,360 --> 00:13:10,560
Even though my heart was still beating,

211
00:13:11,760 --> 00:13:12,880
but my soul

212
00:13:14,760 --> 00:13:16,200
had already left with you.

213
00:13:18,280 --> 00:13:19,240
Don't be silly.

214
00:13:21,520 --> 00:13:23,400
I'm fine now, am I not?

215
00:13:28,480 --> 00:13:29,240
Qi Yan.

216
00:13:30,000 --> 00:13:31,200
Do you know

217
00:13:31,920 --> 00:13:33,680
maybe I'm going to disappear too?

218
00:13:34,680 --> 00:13:36,160
If I disappear,

219
00:13:36,160 --> 00:13:37,280
what's going to happen to you?

220
00:13:38,600 --> 00:13:42,000
Will you suffer in pain like Kong An?

221
00:13:43,960 --> 00:13:44,600
Mengmeng.

222
00:13:49,000 --> 00:13:50,440
No matter what will happen
in the future,

223
00:13:52,120 --> 00:13:53,560
I hope you always remember

224
00:13:55,240 --> 00:13:56,280
that I will love you forever.

225
00:14:11,200 --> 00:14:12,280
Toasting with tea

226
00:14:12,560 --> 00:14:14,360
to celebrate Wan's freedom.

227
00:14:23,640 --> 00:14:24,920
Your Majesty's
sending us off personally.

228
00:14:25,120 --> 00:14:26,000
This way,

229
00:14:27,200 --> 00:14:29,480
isn't the rumor of me
being exiled to the border

230
00:14:29,480 --> 00:14:30,600
going to collapse on itself?

231
00:14:30,880 --> 00:14:32,000
Who spread such rumor?

232
00:14:32,000 --> 00:14:33,000
It's so inaccurate.

233
00:14:33,440 --> 00:14:35,280
Obviously, it is you
who didn't want to see me,

234
00:14:35,400 --> 00:14:36,640
and deliberately ran away
as far as possible.

235
00:14:44,360 --> 00:14:45,920
Didn't you say you wanted to
come and send them off?

236
00:14:46,480 --> 00:14:47,400
Why have you been

237
00:14:47,560 --> 00:14:48,480
so quiet since you came?

238
00:14:49,640 --> 00:14:51,080
Are you too sad to part with me?

239
00:14:51,400 --> 00:14:52,360
You talk too much!

240
00:14:54,920 --> 00:14:55,680
Mengmeng.

241
00:14:55,920 --> 00:14:57,400
We're not gone forever.

242
00:14:57,840 --> 00:14:59,440
I'll write letters to you regularly.

243
00:14:59,720 --> 00:15:01,080
We'll meet again someday.

244
00:15:06,600 --> 00:15:07,280
Li Tao.

245
00:15:09,160 --> 00:15:09,840
What's this?

246
00:15:15,960 --> 00:15:17,280
The underground aqueduct blueprints?

247
00:15:19,880 --> 00:15:20,920
I thought you stingy fellow

248
00:15:20,920 --> 00:15:21,720
wouldn't give it to me.

249
00:15:23,280 --> 00:15:24,600
Why did you suddenly change your mind

250
00:15:25,040 --> 00:15:25,840
and give it to me?

251
00:15:26,760 --> 00:15:28,280
Actually, I wasn't planning
to hide it anyway.

252
00:15:29,200 --> 00:15:31,560
This underground aqueduct blueprints
will benefit the people.

253
00:15:31,920 --> 00:15:33,640
I just don't want the people of Ximi

254
00:15:33,640 --> 00:15:35,120
to suffer from drought.

255
00:15:36,680 --> 00:15:38,720
On behalf of the people of Ximi,
thank you.

256
00:15:41,560 --> 00:15:42,400
No need for formalities.

257
00:15:42,880 --> 00:15:43,840
As long as you

258
00:15:44,200 --> 00:15:45,640
don't come to Qi Kingdom ever again.

259
00:15:47,240 --> 00:15:48,320
That's not possible.

260
00:15:48,760 --> 00:15:49,960
During this stay to Qi Kingdom,

261
00:15:49,960 --> 00:15:51,560
I really learned a lot.

262
00:15:51,920 --> 00:15:52,840
Once the aqueduct is completed,

263
00:15:52,840 --> 00:15:53,520
I'll be back.

264
00:15:53,920 --> 00:15:55,080
Next time you come,

265
00:15:55,440 --> 00:15:57,000
Mengmeng and I will be married.

266
00:15:57,720 --> 00:15:58,280
Alright.

267
00:15:59,120 --> 00:16:01,520
No matter how hard it is,
parting is inevitable.

268
00:16:02,720 --> 00:16:03,480
Let's go.

269
00:16:05,520 --> 00:16:06,320
Wan.

270
00:16:07,640 --> 00:16:09,160
Do we really have to part?

271
00:16:09,960 --> 00:16:11,480
I can't be without you.

272
00:16:12,320 --> 00:16:13,080
Mengmeng.

273
00:16:13,720 --> 00:16:14,880
We'll meet many people

274
00:16:14,880 --> 00:16:16,440
in our life.

275
00:16:17,000 --> 00:16:18,280
Most of them

276
00:16:18,560 --> 00:16:20,520
will only be with us for a while.

277
00:16:20,760 --> 00:16:23,560
So, we should cherish them even more,
shouldn't we?

278
00:16:23,560 --> 00:16:25,600
But we only have two hands.

279
00:16:25,960 --> 00:16:27,000
Just two hands.

280
00:16:27,240 --> 00:16:28,320
How can we hold onto

281
00:16:28,320 --> 00:16:29,880
everything we want?

282
00:16:31,320 --> 00:16:33,000
Perhaps sometimes

283
00:16:33,520 --> 00:16:35,400
being brave to face farewells

284
00:16:35,760 --> 00:16:37,440
and saying goodbye gracefully

285
00:16:38,320 --> 00:16:40,360
is also a good choice.

286
00:16:40,960 --> 00:16:41,560
Right?

