288
00:16:44,940 --> 00:16:48,300
♪Before I come to you♪

289
00:16:48,840 --> 00:16:49,640
Mengmeng.

290
00:16:50,760 --> 00:16:51,840
Take care.

291
00:16:52,440 --> 00:16:53,440
You too.

