311
00:17:54,400 --> 00:17:54,920
Your Majesty.

312
00:17:55,440 --> 00:17:57,160
Cui Anshi, Cui Anzu, Cui Anyu,

313
00:17:57,160 --> 00:17:57,960
have all confessed.

314
00:17:58,360 --> 00:17:59,720
The officials involved in the rebellion

315
00:17:59,720 --> 00:18:00,760
