322
00:18:12,160 --> 00:18:14,080
Cui Anshi has wielded
immense power for many years,

323
00:18:14,320 --> 00:18:16,000
and his influence is deeply rooted.

324
00:18:16,320 --> 00:18:18,360
There's no need to
delve further into this matter.

325
00:18:19,640 --> 00:18:21,320
As for those involved in the rebellion,

326
00:18:21,560 --> 00:18:23,480
they can be dealt with
according to the law.

327
00:18:23,480 --> 00:18:24,040
Alright.

328
00:18:27,320 --> 00:18:28,680
Has Mengmeng had her meal today?

329
00:18:29,000 --> 00:18:29,840
Your Majesty,

330
00:18:30,080 --> 00:18:32,080
the people from Lingtai Pavilion
came over today

331
00:18:32,080 --> 00:18:33,320
and said she only ate a little.

332
00:18:34,600 --> 00:18:35,760
Let's go and have a look.

333
00:18:35,880 --> 00:18:36,560
Yes.

334
00:18:59,880 --> 00:19:00,760
The Emissary has been like this

335
00:19:00,760 --> 00:19:02,000
