346
00:19:25,960 --> 00:19:26,560
Well...

347
00:19:28,640 --> 00:19:29,240
Your Majesty.

348
00:19:29,240 --> 00:19:30,280
As you know,

349
00:19:30,440 --> 00:19:32,120
