is so extraordinary.

350
00:19:32,360 --> 00:19:34,040
What new things hasn't she seen before?

351
00:19:34,240 --> 00:19:35,040
Over here...

352
00:19:38,760 --> 00:19:40,560
Perhaps what she wants
