362
00:20:16,640 --> 00:20:18,080
The soup is already prepared.

363
00:20:19,680 --> 00:20:21,320
Bring in the soup!

364
00:20:35,560 --> 00:20:36,160
Your Majesty.

365
00:20:36,520 --> 00:20:37,760
These are made
with the finest ingredients

366
00:20:37,760 --> 00:20:39,360
by the imperial kitchen.

367
00:20:55,560 --> 00:20:58,680
Add this and this to that.

368
00:20:59,520 --> 00:21:00,800
Then it should be about right.

369
00:21:01,640 --> 00:21:02,200
Yes.

370
00:21:03,160 --> 00:21:03,840
Your Majesty.

371
00:21:04,080 --> 00:21:05,760
What about the other soups?

372
00:21:09,040 --> 00:21:10,080
Can you finish it?

373
00:21:11,200 --> 00:21:12,760
Thank you. Your Majesty.

374
00:21:22,640 --> 00:21:23,280
Come on.

375
00:21:24,160 --> 00:21:26,680
Guess what I've prepared for you.

376
00:21:30,840 --> 00:21:31,400
Sit.

377
00:21:34,560 --> 00:21:35,800
What is this?

378
00:21:35,800 --> 00:21:37,200
It's so mysterious.

379
00:21:41,960 --> 00:21:44,080
Doesn't this look like

380
00:21:44,080 --> 00:21:45,160
