381
00:21:47,800 --> 00:21:48,800
Well...

382
00:21:48,800 --> 00:21:51,000
This is even better than
the "Buddha's Temptation" from my hometown

383
00:21:51,440 --> 00:21:52,240
Buddha's Temptation?

384
00:21:52,480 --> 00:21:53,200
How is it made?

385
00:21:53,260 --> 00:21:54,080
Let me know.

386
00:21:54,100 --> 00:21:55,840
I'll ask the imperial kitchen
to make it.

387
00:21:56,200 --> 00:21:57,120
No. It's fine.

388
00:21:57,480 --> 00:21:58,960
This is really good enough.

389
00:22:00,200 --> 00:22:00,760
Come on.

390
00:22:01,640 --> 00:22:02,720
Go ahead and taste it.

391
00:22:08,640 --> 00:22:09,440
Come on, taste it.

392
00:22:18,000 --> 00:22:18,720
Delicious.

393
00:22:21,640 --> 00:22:22,440
I...

394
00:22:22,800 --> 00:22:24,800
have some other surprises for you.

395
00:22:30,840 --> 00:22:31,240
Come on.

396
00:22:31,960 --> 00:22:32,800
They're about to start.

397
00:22:34,600 --> 00:22:35,160
Look.

398
00:22:40,440 --> 00:22:41,800
Isn't this the classic scene

399
00:22:41,800 --> 00:22:43,680
I told them before?

400
00:22:43,840 --> 00:22:44,720
They even made the pistol

401
00:22:44,720 --> 00:22:46,280
that I drew last time.

402
00:22:47,160 --> 00:22:48,160
You're pretty smooth.

403
00:22:49,520 --> 00:22:52,160
I underwent professional training
before entering the palace.

404
00:22:52,480 --> 00:22:54,160
You temple folks are so interesting,

405
00:22:54,800 --> 00:22:56,320
always choose to meet on the rooftop.

406
00:22:57,160 --> 00:22:58,240
Temple folks?

407
00:22:58,400 --> 00:22:59,640
I'm not like you.

408
00:22:59,640 --> 00:23:01,360
I used to be a temple folk too.

409
00:23:01,960 --> 00:23:03,520
Did you bring what I asked for?

410
00:23:04,720 --> 00:23:06,200
You might not have brought

411
00:23:06,200 --> 00:23:07,400
what I asked for either.

412
00:23:09,800 --> 00:23:10,320
What?

413
00:23:11,400 --> 00:23:12,520
Coming up here for a sunbathe?

414
00:23:14,120 --> 00:23:14,960
Give me a chance.

415
00:23:16,560 --> 00:23:17,200
How so?

416
00:23:18,160 --> 00:23:19,800
They're acting so seriously.

417
00:23:20,640 --> 00:23:22,240
Look at Steward Lu's beard.

418
00:23:23,080 --> 00:23:24,160
I had no choice before,

419
00:23:24,760 --> 00:23:26,080
but now I want to be a good person.

420
00:23:28,760 --> 00:23:29,360
Alright.

421
00:23:30,000 --> 00:23:30,920
Go ask His Majesty.

422
00:23:31,600 --> 00:23:32,920
See if he allows you
to be a good person.

423
00:23:33,560 --> 00:23:34,760
