427
00:23:46,120 --> 00:23:48,120
Steward Lu, I really couldn't resist.

428
00:23:49,120 --> 00:23:50,480
You know what?

429
00:23:50,640 --> 00:23:52,640
Based on Steward Lu's acting skills,

430
00:23:52,640 --> 00:23:54,120
if he was in my hometown,

431
00:23:54,120 --> 00:23:56,040
he'd definitely
be an award-winning actor.

432
00:23:57,560 --> 00:23:58,280
Faster.

433
00:23:58,840 --> 00:23:59,680
Change the scene.

434
00:23:59,960 --> 00:24:00,520
Yes.

435
00:24:01,240 --> 00:24:01,920
There's more?

436
00:24:06,440 --> 00:24:07,000
Mengmeng.

437
00:24:07,400 --> 00:24:08,920
Let me tell you some good news.

438
00:24:09,000 --> 00:24:10,640
Minister Li's watercourse plan

439
00:24:10,640 --> 00:24:12,280
