in the Suzhou section.

440
00:24:12,280 --> 00:24:13,160
Really?

441
00:24:13,360 --> 00:24:14,120
He'd definitely be very happy

442
00:24:14,120 --> 00:24:15,400
if he knew it.

443
00:24:19,160 --> 00:24:21,000
Thank you for today.

444
00:24:22,280 --> 00:24:23,600
I'm very happy today.

445
00:24:24,640 --> 00:24:25,800
I watched TV,

446
00:24:25,920 --> 00:24:26,880
ate instant noodles,

447
00:24:27,200 --> 00:24:28,400
and had popcorn.

448
00:24:29,680 --> 00:24:30,720
It feels like

449
00:24:31,040 --> 00:24:32,200
being at home.

450
00:24:35,640 --> 00:24:36,280
Mengmeng.

451
00:24:40,080 --> 00:24:41,240
Do you still remember this?

452
00:24:45,760 --> 00:24:46,840
In the past,

453
00:24:47,880 --> 00:24:49,480
I never thought about
what my future empress

454
00:24:49,480 --> 00:24:50,400
would be like.

455
00:24:53,600 --> 00:24:54,880
But now I know.

456
00:24:57,120 --> 00:24:58,320
My future wife

457
00:24:59,680 --> 00:25:00,760
has a round face,

458
00:25:02,080 --> 00:25:03,080
a round nose,

459
00:25:04,760 --> 00:25:06,200
and eyes like crescent moons.

460
00:25:06,880 --> 00:25:07,640
When she smiles,

461
00:25:08,280 --> 00:25:09,600
her eyes turn into slits.

462
00:25:12,440 --> 00:25:13,520
She's petite,

463
00:25:14,680 --> 00:25:15,680
but quite strong.

464
00:25:19,400 --> 00:25:21,280
She's always full of ideas

465
00:25:22,160 --> 00:25:23,960
and always has surprises for me.

466
00:25:25,120 --> 00:25:25,720
Mengmeng.

467
00:25:33,520 --> 00:25:34,320
Marry me.

468
00:25:35,760 --> 00:25:37,800
Mother has already
arranged our marriage.

469
00:25:38,400 --> 00:25:39,760
This is my request

470
00:25:41,680 --> 00:25:42,520
and also a royal decree.

471
00:25:48,600 --> 00:25:49,600
But...

472
00:25:50,520 --> 00:25:53,640
What if one day I have to leave?

473
00:25:56,680 --> 00:25:59,160
What if something unexpected
happens to me

474
00:25:59,160 --> 00:25:59,960
or I fall ill?

475
00:25:59,960 --> 00:26:01,000
Stop talking nonsense!

476
00:26:05,280 --> 00:26:06,720
I don't care what the future holds.

477
00:26:07,960 --> 00:26:09,000
If there's only one day,

478
00:26:10,360 --> 00:26:12,120
you'll be my wife for one day.

479
00:26:12,800 --> 00:26:13,640
If there are two days,

480
00:26:14,000 --> 00:26:15,640
you'll be my wife for two days.

481
00:26:19,160 --> 00:26:20,360
As long as I'm here,

482
00:26:21,560 --> 00:26:22,720
as long as you're still here,

483
00:26:24,280 --> 00:26:25,840
we'll be together every day.

484
00:27:05,140 --> 00:27:06,920
[Wanshou Hall]

485
00:27:06,920 --> 00:27:09,960
By the grace of Heaven,
the Emperor decrees:

486
00:27:09,960 --> 00:27:13,040
[Imperial Decree]
Chancellor Cui Anshi neglected his duties,

487
00:27:13,040 --> 00:27:14,440
abused his power for personal gain,

488
00:27:14,440 --> 00:27:16,000
embezzled disaster relief supplies,

489
00:27:16,000 --> 00:27:17,360
raised private armies,

490
00:27:17,360 --> 00:27:18,560
and plotted rebellion,

491
00:27:18,560 --> 00:27:20,600
showing great disrespect
to the ancestral temples and altars.

492
00:27:20,600 --> 00:27:23,800
The mastermind, Chancellor Cui Anshi,

493
00:27:23,800 --> 00:27:25,800
the leader of the Imperial Guards,
Cui Anyu,

494
00:27:25,800 --> 00:27:27,880
along with thirteen others,
are sentenced to death.

495
00:27:27,880 --> 00:27:30,800
All assets within their households will
be confiscated for the national treasury.

496
00:27:30,800 --> 00:27:33,240
Their families will be demoted
to commoners

497
00:27:33,240 --> 00:27:35,560
and prohibited from serving as officials
in the palace for three generations.

498
00:27:35,560 --> 00:27:39,080
Thirty-seven others involved
in the rebellion

499
00:27:39,080 --> 00:27:40,360
will have their official status stripped

500
00:27:40,360 --> 00:27:41,720
and be exiled to Lingnan.

501
00:27:41,720 --> 00:27:43,200
End of reading.

502
00:27:43,760 --> 00:27:46,440
Your Majesty's wisdom shines brightly.

503
00:27:47,320 --> 00:27:49,320
There is another matter
to announce today.

504
00:27:50,360 --> 00:27:50,920
Lu Huan.

505
00:27:51,400 --> 00:27:51,960
Yes.

506
00:27:58,320 --> 00:28:01,360
By the grace of the heavens,
the Emperor decrees:

507
00:28:01,360 --> 00:28:02,960
The Emissary, Li Mengmeng,

508
00:28:02,960 --> 00:28:04,200
who is intelligent and astute,

509
00:28:04,200 --> 00:28:05,400
speaks and acts
with propriety and moderation,

510
00:28:05,400 --> 00:28:06,920
and possesses a great character,

511
00:28:06,920 --> 00:28:09,480
She shall be conferred the title
of the Empress Consort.

512
00:28:09,480 --> 00:28:11,040
End of reading.

513
00:28:12,480 --> 00:28:13,400
But...

514
00:28:13,400 --> 00:28:14,280
This might not be appropriate.

515
00:28:14,280 --> 00:28:15,160
Your Majesty.

516
00:28:15,160 --> 00:28:17,480
Since the founding of Qi Kingdom,

517
00:28:17,480 --> 00:28:19,840
the Empress Consorts have always come
from noble families,

518
00:28:19,960 --> 00:28:21,080
exemplifying dignity and humility,

519
00:28:21,080 --> 00:28:22,520
upholding ceremonial propriety.

520
00:28:22,520 --> 00:28:24,560
This Emissary, she disguised as a man,

521
00:28:24,560 --> 00:28:26,080
first as an eunuch,

522
00:28:26,080 --> 00:28:29,160
then as a man,
entering the Lingtai Pavilion.

523
00:28:29,160 --> 00:28:30,440
She has reckless demeanor.

524
00:28:30,720 --> 00:28:32,080
If she becomes
the Empress of the kingdom,

525
00:28:32,080 --> 00:28:34,000
it would be a disgrace
to our traditions.

526
00:28:34,200 --> 00:28:36,400
Your Majesty, please reconsider.

527
00:28:36,400 --> 00:28:39,600
Your Majesty, please reconsider.

528
00:28:39,680 --> 00:28:40,440
Traditions?

529
00:28:42,240 --> 00:28:43,160
If it weren't for her,

530
00:28:43,800 --> 00:28:45,480
the aqueduct would not have been built,

531
00:28:45,840 --> 00:28:48,040
and countless people
would have suffered from drought.

532
00:28:48,040 --> 00:28:49,040
If it weren't for her,

533
00:28:49,040 --> 00:28:50,000
on the day of the sacrifice,

534
00:28:50,000 --> 00:28:52,400
I would have perished in the fire.

535
00:28:53,400 --> 00:28:55,440
Besides, this is the dowry from mother.

536
00:28:56,560 --> 00:28:58,040
I have already recognized her as...

537
00:28:58,800 --> 00:29:00,240
my only wife in this life.

538
00:29:02,200 --> 00:29:02,880
Lu Huan.

539
00:29:03,200 --> 00:29:03,600
Yes.

540
00:29:04,160 --> 00:29:05,320
Convey the decree.

541
00:29:05,320 --> 00:29:07,840
Complete the enthronement ceremony
within three days.

542
00:29:07,840 --> 00:29:08,520
Yes.

543
00:29:08,760 --> 00:29:09,240
Well...

544
00:29:09,640 --> 00:29:10,640
Your Majesty...

545
00:29:10,640 --> 00:29:12,400
As the noble ruler of our kingdom,

546
00:29:12,400 --> 00:29:14,520
marriage is not just a personal matter,

547
00:29:14,520 --> 00:29:15,720
but also a national affair.

548
00:29:15,720 --> 00:29:17,720
How can we act recklessly?

549
00:29:18,000 --> 00:29:19,240
In all my years,

550
00:29:20,360 --> 00:29:21,640
everything I've done

551
00:29:22,120 --> 00:29:23,920
has been bound
by the nation's laws and rules.

552
00:29:24,440 --> 00:29:25,440
Except for this time,

553
00:29:26,920 --> 00:29:28,480
I want to be stubborn for once.

554
00:29:28,560 --> 00:29:29,240
Your Majesty...

555
00:29:29,800 --> 00:29:31,360
If you truly like the Emissary,

556
00:29:31,360 --> 00:29:32,480
you can take her into the harem,

557
00:29:32,720 --> 00:29:34,600
but her status must not be elevated.

558
00:29:34,600 --> 00:29:35,800
It must not, Your Majesty.

559
00:29:36,000 --> 00:29:37,360
If you insist on this,

560
00:29:37,360 --> 00:29:39,520
I would feel ashamed
before our ancestors.

561
00:29:39,680 --> 00:29:42,160
Your Majesty, please reconsider.

562
00:29:42,160 --> 00:29:45,080
Your Majesty, please reconsider.

563
00:29:45,560 --> 00:29:46,600
My mind is made up.

564
00:29:49,560 --> 00:29:50,080
Your Majesty!

565
00:29:50,640 --> 00:29:52,320
Your Majesty, please reconsider.

566
00:29:53,000 --> 00:29:53,560
Your Majesty...

567
00:29:53,560 --> 00:29:55,000
The morning audience is dismissed.

