00:30:04,380 --> 00:30:06,980
[Qingyan Palace]

570
00:30:08,820 --> 00:30:12,140
[Qingyan Hall]

571
00:30:20,120 --> 00:30:21,000
Minister Sun.

572
00:30:21,120 --> 00:30:21,840
What's going on?

573
00:30:21,840 --> 00:30:23,680
Summon the imperial physician, now!

574
00:30:25,320 --> 00:30:25,920
Your Majesty.

575
00:30:26,480 --> 00:30:27,160
Your Majesty.

576
00:30:28,000 --> 00:30:28,600
Your Majesty.

577
00:30:30,240 --> 00:30:31,040
What's happening outside?

578
00:30:31,200 --> 00:30:33,080
Minister Sun fainted just now,

579
00:30:33,240 --> 00:30:35,560
but the imperial physician
has treated him in time.

580
00:30:35,560 --> 00:30:36,560
He's fine now.

581
00:30:38,880 --> 00:30:40,840
Have the imperial physician center
send people to take turns watching him.

582
00:30:41,080 --> 00:30:43,040
Also, prepare meals
from the Imperial Kitchen.

583
00:30:43,040 --> 00:30:43,640
Yes.

584
00:30:43,880 --> 00:30:45,560
Did you convey the orders
to the Lingtai Pavilion?

585
00:30:45,920 --> 00:30:47,880
I don't want Mengmeng
to be bothered before the wedding.

586
00:30:48,440 --> 00:30:49,920
I have already instructed them.

587
00:30:50,120 --> 00:30:51,880
Don't let Miss Mengmeng know about this.

588
00:30:52,480 --> 00:30:54,840
But if she insists on seeing you,

589
00:30:55,640 --> 00:30:56,720
we'll tell her that

590
00:30:56,720 --> 00:30:59,760
Husband and wife are not allowed
to meet three days before the wedding.

591
00:31:03,480 --> 00:31:04,800
Husband and wife?

592
00:31:38,820 --> 00:31:42,060
♪When a gust of wind brushes past♪

593
00:31:42,060 --> 00:31:45,620
♪The sand and wind burn with passion♪

594
00:31:45,620 --> 00:31:48,700
♪Unafraid to forego a chance
to quench our thirst♪

595
00:31:48,700 --> 00:31:52,500
♪Like camels walking with eyes closed♪

596
00:31:52,500 --> 00:31:55,620
♪When the rain falls
into a rare silence♪

597
00:31:55,620 --> 00:31:59,340
♪Thinking of hardships
you and I don't know♪

598
00:31:59,340 --> 00:32:02,340
♪No need to hum the wind's song♪

599
00:32:02,340 --> 00:32:06,420
♪Uncaring of the darkening skies♪

600
00:32:06,420 --> 00:32:08,100
♪I understood all that for you♪

601
00:32:08,100 --> 00:32:09,860
♪But you have disappeared♪

602
00:32:09,860 --> 00:32:11,540
♪I am lost in the dark♪

603
00:32:11,540 --> 00:32:13,260
♪How should I stop?♪

604
00:32:13,260 --> 00:32:14,940
♪Loving you feels like another lifetime♪

605
00:32:14,940 --> 00:32:18,620
♪But yearning flows into a poem♪

606
00:32:18,620 --> 00:32:21,580
♪For us to meet again♪

607
00:32:21,580 --> 00:32:24,940
♪Requires the promise of a millennia♪

608
00:32:24,940 --> 00:32:27,180
♪Watching the rain hail down♪

609
00:32:27,180 --> 00:32:32,260
♪It's like you're still beside me♪

610
00:32:32,260 --> 00:32:35,220
♪When I want to cross over♪

611
00:32:35,220 --> 00:32:39,300
♪To touch you♪

612
00:32:39,300 --> 00:32:41,740
♪But I can't see your fading face♪

613
00:32:41,740 --> 00:32:46,020
♪On the opposite shore♪

614
00:32:46,020 --> 00:32:49,020
♪How do I voice this?♪

615
00:32:49,020 --> 00:32:52,420
♪My heart beats uneasily♪

616
00:32:52,420 --> 00:32:55,340
♪How I long to hold tight♪

617
00:32:55,340 --> 00:32:59,700
♪To the loneliness in your hands♪

618
00:32:59,700 --> 00:33:02,700
♪Yet you warn me♪

619
00:33:02,700 --> 00:33:06,740
♪Any closer and I'll be set in stone♪

620
00:33:06,740 --> 00:33:08,340
♪The sunset deep in your heart♪

621
00:33:08,340 --> 00:33:16,220
♪Of the day you most loved me♪
